newsLetters.heading: Hocus Pocus
newsLetters.paragraph: Pair a Plain, Rosemary, or Cinnamon Raisin bagel with a cream cheese or chive schmear for a tasty breakfast on-the-go, or  grab our new White Cheddar and Prosciutto Grilled Cheese! We're slinging these bad boys all day from 8am until the hour before closing time.
